| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1828 — Recovery Inhibition (apt73)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9f7b8f62-bd07-5cf9-accf-c3d20cc31ee9"
